      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britains-tesco-expects-profit-rise-202425-year-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大零售商乐购 (Tesco) 预计新财年利润将进一步增长，强劲需求和新客户帮助其 2023/24 年利润增长 11%。]]></description>
